    <item>
      <title>特朗普加速竞选 哈里斯呼吁支持者“战斗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/harris-urges-supporters-to-fight-as-trump-accelerates-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯开始了宾夕法尼亚州的巴士之旅，在这个关键战场州号召志愿者，而她的共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普则宣布计划加大政治活动的节奏，以阻止她的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/harris-urges-supporters-to-fight-as-trump-accelerates-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 19:52:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将访问边境，以反击哈里斯在大会上的讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/trump-to-visit-border-in-bid-to-counter-harris-convention-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人唐纳德·特朗普将于本周晚些时候前往美墨边境，这是他的竞选活动加大政治压力并吸引卡玛拉·哈里斯注意力的举措之一，因为民主党在芝加哥全国代表大会上庆祝她获得总统候选人提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/trump-to-visit-border-in-bid-to-counter-harris-convention-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 18:38:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯前往芝加哥，势头强劲，共和党批评声不断升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/harris-heads-to-chicago-with-momentum-and-gop-criticism-rising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 正乘势前往民主党全国代表大会，而共和党则试图通过攻击她的新经济议程来赢得选民支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/harris-heads-to-chicago-with-momentum-and-gop-criticism-rising</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:00:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列和哈马斯互相指责对方破坏停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/netanyahu-seeks-to-place-responsibility-with-hamas-for-a-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国最高外交官抵达特拉维夫敦促达成协议之际，以色列和哈马斯互相指责对方阻碍停火和人质协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/netanyahu-seeks-to-place-responsibility-with-hamas-for-a-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非议会将讨论 Eskom 的能源成本上涨计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/south-african-parliament-to-debate-eskom-s-energy-cost-hike-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据民主联盟党发表声明称，南非议会将对该国国有能源公司的一项提案进行辩论，该提案可能导致明年电价上涨高达 40%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/south-african-parliament-to-debate-eskom-s-energy-cost-hike-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚石油公司签署法令禁止向以色列出口煤炭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/colombia-s-petro-signs-decree-banning-coal-exports-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗签署法令，禁止向以色列出口煤炭，以向总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡的政府施压，结束加沙冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/colombia-s-petro-signs-decree-banning-coal-exports-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚中央银行因员工被绑架而暂停运营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/libya-central-bank-suspends-operations-after-employee-kidnapped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚央行表示，在一名高级职员周日被绑架后，该行已暂停业务，这是十多年来政治纷争造成的安全真空使这个欧佩克国家陷入更深混乱的最新例证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/libya-central-bank-suspends-operations-after-employee-kidnapped</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 12:16:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普抨击哈里斯通胀问题，转而嘲笑她的笑声</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/trump-jabs-harris-on-inflation-before-pivoting-to-her-laugh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普曾试图将副总统卡马拉·哈里斯与总统乔·拜登执政期间的高通胀联系起来，随后转向即兴的批评，他表示盟友敦促他避免这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/trump-jabs-harris-on-inflation-before-pivoting-to-her-laugh</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 22:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赤道几内亚领导人任命前银行家打击腐败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/equatorial-guinea-leader-taps-ex-banker-to-fix-economic-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赤道几内亚任命曼努埃尔·奥萨·恩苏埃·恩苏埃为总理。三周前，上届政府因未能解决包括政府腐败在内的国家经济困境而被解散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/equatorial-guinea-leader-taps-ex-banker-to-fix-economic-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 13:48:29 GMT</pubDate>
